                    <span>After reading Theodore Rex, I was sold and I wanted to learn more about the great president.  This book starts off with his birth and works up to Theordore Rex, which highlights Teddy's years in the White House.
<br />
<br />I found this book to be very detailed and interesting.  The only book I can recommend more than this one is Theodore Rex, which is by the same author.  It'd be better to read this one first and then move on.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">It just does not get any better than this!</div>
